Description:

Collette is a passionate French girl who is looking for sex in all the wrong places. She goes to a shrink (played by the actor turned District Attorney Guy Thomas) to talk about her obsession but he is no help as he is too preoccupied with his own head nurse. Then she seeks the help of a cult priest but realizes he has no answers, either. She tries a threesome with her oversexed girlfriend but ultimately it is the unexpected entrance of a mysterious man in a cape and top hat that finally helps Collette realize her sexual ambitions
